OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLate sunny
OL,6,Fthen clear spells and a few scattered
OL,7,Fshowers, some of which may be wintry
OL,8,Fover Shetland. A cold night with a
OL,9,Ftouch of frost. Light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FA bright and mainly dry
OL,12,Fday, with some sunny interludes. Still
OL,13,Fthe chance of a few light showers,
OL,14,Fmainly over Shetland. Turning cloudy
OL,15,Fduring evening, patchy rain overnight.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,18,FBright but with good deal of cloud
OL,19,Faround during this period and a few
OL,20,Fscattered showers. Rather breezy at
OL,21,Ftimes.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
